"Trieu <span class=\"menuchoice\"> <span class=\"guimenu\">Aplicacions</"
"span>&nbsp;▸ <span class=\"guisubmenu\">Eines del sistema</span>&nbsp;▸ "
"<span class=\"guimenuitem\">Terminal d'administrador</span> </span> per "
