#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuring additional APT repositories  (for advanced users)"
msgstr "Configuració de repositoris APT addicionals (per a usuaris avançats)"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>The packages available in Debian are\n"
"submitted to public scrutiny.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Els paquets disponibles a Debian són\n"
"sotmesos a l'escrutini públic.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>Configuring additional APT repositories might break the security built in\n"
"Tails and might install software that has not even been approved by Debian. Be even more careful\n"
"with what you install.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>La configuració de repositoris APT addicionals pot trencar la seguretat integrada\n"
"a Tails i podria instal·lar programari que ni tan sols ha estat aprovat per Debian. Tingueu encara més cura\n"
"amb el que instal·leu.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"<p>This step is usually not needed to install additional software and might be necessary\n"
"only in very rare occasions.</p>\n"
msgstr ""
"<p>Aquest pas normalment no és necessari per instal·lar programari addicional i pot ser necessari\n"
"només en ocasions molt rares.</p>\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Sometimes, you might need to configure additional APT repositories. For "
"example, to install packages from the `non-free` section of Debian. To do so:"
msgstr ""
"De vegades, és possible que hàgiu de configurar repositoris APT addicionals. "
"Per exemple, per instal·lar paquets des de la secció `no lliure` de Debian. "
"Per fer-ho:"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Create an <span class=\"filename\">apt-sources.list.d</span> folder in your "
"Persistent Storage:"
msgstr ""
"Creeu una carpeta <span class=\"filename\">apt-sources.list.d</span> al "
"vostre Emmagatzematge Persistent:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "   <p class=\"command\">sudo install -d -m 755 /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d</p>\n"
msgstr "   <p class=\"command\">sudo install -d -m 755 /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d</p>\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"As root, edit */live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/persistence.conf*, the "
"configuration of the Persistent Storage, and add the *apt-sources.list.d* "
"folder as a feature of type `link`:"
msgstr ""
"Com a administrador, editeu */live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/"
"persistence.conf*, la configuració de l'Emmagatzematge Persistent, i afegiu "
"la carpeta *apt-sources.list.d* com a funcionalitat del tipus `link`:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "       /etc/apt/sources.list.d\tsource=apt-sources.list.d,link\n"
msgstr "       /etc/apt/sources.list.d\tsource=apt-sources.list.d,link\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Write your additional `sources.list` files in the *apt-sources.list.d* "
"folder."
msgstr ""
"Escriviu els vostres fitxers `sources.list` addicionals a la carpeta *apt-"
"sources.list.d*."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   For example, to add\n"
"   the `non-free` sections of Debian 11 (Bullseye), backports, and security\n"
"   updates, you can create a file named\n"
"   */live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list*\n"
"   with the following content:\n"
msgstr ""
"   Per exemple, per afegir\n"
"   les seccions `no lliures` de Debian 11 (Bullseye), backports i actualitzacions de\n"
"   seguretat, podeu crear un fitxer anomenat\n"
"   */live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list*\n"
"   amb el contingut següent:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       deb tor+http://ftp.us.debian.org/debian/ bullseye non-free\n"
"       deb tor+http://ftp.us.debian.org/debian/ bullseye-backports non-free\n"
"       deb tor+http://security.debian.org/ bullseye/updates non-free\n"
msgstr ""
"       deb tor+http://ftp.us.debian.org/debian/ bullseye non-free\n"
"       deb tor+http://ftp.us.debian.org/debian/ bullseye-backports non-free\n"
"       deb tor+http://security.debian.org/ bullseye/updates non-free\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"   File names must end with *.list* and must only contain the following\n"
"   characters: letters, digits, underscore, hyphen, and period.\n"
msgstr ""
"   Els noms dels fitxers han d'acabar amb *.list* i només han de contenir els següents\n"
"   caràcters: lletres, dígits, guió baix, guionet i punt.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '1. '
msgid ""
"Correct the ownership and permissions of your additional `sources.list` "
"files to be owned by `root` and only readable by others. For example:"
msgstr ""
"Corregiu la propietat i els permisos dels vostres fitxers `sources.list` "
"addicionals perquè siguin propietat de `root` i només els puguin llegir "
"altres. Per exemple:"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"       chown root:root /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list\n"
"       chmod 644 /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list\n"
msgstr ""
"       chown root:root /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list\n"
"       chmod 644 /live/persistence/TailsData_unlocked/apt-sources.list.d/non-free.list\n"

